                <li class="standing__committee--item">
                    Standing Committee on IT & IMS
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>                    
        <br>

        <div class="margin_boo">
            <p class="areas__content">
              AREAS has been granted registration on 25th July 2016, as General Public Utility Trust/Society u/s 12AA(1)(b) read with section 12A of the Income Tax act, 1961 to allow for its exemption from taxation.<br> It has also received approval u/s 80G of the Income Tax Act, 1961 on 25th July 2016 to allow for specified tax benefit to Donors. These exemptions/benefits are valid from Annual Year 2016-17 onwards.</p>
